OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with some light
OL,6,Fshowers. Cloud breaking to give some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells into the
OL,8,Fafternoon but with further showers,
OL,9,Flocally heavy and could be thundery in
OL,10,Fthe south. Feeling warm in sunshine
OL,11,Fand light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers will slowly ease into
OL,14,Fthe evening, with breaks in the cloud
OL,15,Fdeveloping overnight which could see
OL,16,Fsome fog patches developing. Winds
OL,17,Fremain light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
