OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSaturday, bright start but
OL,6,Fshowers developing later some of these
OL,7,Fcould be heavy at times. The wind
OL,8,Fbecomes northeasterly and breezy
OL,9,Fovernight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA band
OL,12,Fof rain clearing south early on
OL,13,FSunday, with brighter skies following.
OL,14,FFurther showers Monday. Often breezy
OL,15,Fand feeling cooler. Tuesday cloudy and
OL,16,Fdry with isolated light showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
